OL,5,Chumiliating'
OL,7,FA refugee has spoken anonymously about
OL,8,Fthe "disgusting and humiliating"
OL,9,Fconditions he faced at a migrant
OL,10,Fprocessing facility.
OL,12,F'Ahmed', is one of 96 people taking
OL,13,Fthe Government to High Court, after
OL,14,Ftheir time at Manston House, Kent, in
OL,15,FSeptember and October 2022.
OL,17,FLarge numbers, including families with
OL,18,Fchildren, pregnant women, and
OL,19,Fvulnerable adults with medical
OL,20,Fconditions, stayed at the centre while
OL,21,Fit was overcrowded and understaffed.
