OL,7,FIn the autumn of 2022, the centre was
OL,8,Fdangerously overcapacity - not because
OL,9,Fof an unexpected surge in channel
OL,10,Fcrossings, but because the processing
OL,11,Fsystem had slowed down.
OL,13,FIn their High Court claim, 96 people
OL,14,Fhave said that by detaining them, the
OL,15,FHome Secretary went beyond legal
OL,16,Fpowers, and their treatment was
OL,17,Finhuman and degrading.
OL,19,FManston House was designed so that
OL,20,Fpeople would stay there for 24 hours,
OL,21,Fbut Ahmed was there for 24 days.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
