OL,7,FHigh Court judges will decide if by
OL,8,Fkeeping people there for so long, the
OL,9,FGovernment broke its own detention
OL,10,Fpolicy.
OL,12,FAhmed has since been granted refugee
OL,13,Fstatus and conditions at Manston have
OL,14,Fimproved.
OL,16,FAhmed had travelled by boat to Turkey,
OL,17,Fthen walked across Europe, and
OL,18,Ftravelled in a dinghy across the
OL,19,Fchannel for 10 hours. When he arrived
OL,20,Fin Dover, he was taken to Manston for
OL,21,Fprocessing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
