OL,7,F"I heard, they put you in a detention
OL,8,Fcentre to check that you are not a
OL,9,Fcriminal in the UK, and then they will
OL,10,Fput us in the hotel to start the
OL,11,Fprocess," Ahmed said.
OL,13,F"They just put a tent and they put you
OL,14,Finside without any preparation and it
OL,15,Fwas a countless number of tents.
OL,17,F"It was very disgusting and very
OL,18,Fhumiliating and very bad and hopeless.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
