OL,7,F"That night in Kent, it was very cold,
OL,8,Fit was in October. They didn't give us
OL,9,Fany blankets and we were on the floor.
OL,10,FI was freezing that night, but I was
OL,11,Fhoping that was only for one night."
OL,13,FComing to the UK on a small boat is
OL,14,Fillegal, to which Ahmed said: "Illegal
OL,15,Fis not like you are inhuman, people
OL,16,Fhave the right to claim asylum. They
OL,17,Fcannot treat you like an animal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
