OL,7,F"(England) is a very nice country, and
OL,8,Fwhen I was released, I see it,
OL,9,Feverybody is welcoming and everybody
OL,10,Fis wanting to take care of themselves
OL,11,Fwant to live a normal life."
OL,13,FThomas Munns, a Caseworker at Duncan
OL,14,FLewis Solicitors "It's sometimes hard
OL,15,Fto find words (to describe the
OL,16,Fconditions at Manston), having read
OL,17,Fsome of the witness statements and the
OL,18,Faccounts that have been given by
OL,19,Fclients.
