OL,7,FThere were outbreaks of scabies
OL,8,Fgastroenteritis and one person died of
OL,9,Fdiphtheria.
OL,11,FThe last hearing at the High Court
OL,12,Fgranted anonymity to all 96 claimants.
OL,14,FAhmed and 95 other people claim they
OL,15,Fwere put in overcrowded, unhygienic
OL,16,Fand unsafe conditions to constitute
OL,17,Finhumane or degrading treatment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
