OL,7,FThere are very few images of what the
OL,8,Finside of Manston House looks like
OL,9,Fbecause everyone taken there had their
OL,10,Fphone taken away.
OL,12,FThe court case is ongoing, and the
OL,13,Fnext hearing is scheduled for 23
OL,14,FOctober 2024.
OL,16,FITV News Meridian asked the Home
OL,17,FOffice for a comment, but a
OL,18,Fspokesperson said, as court
OL,19,Fproceedings are active, "it would be
OL,20,Finappropriate to comment."
